Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.99,0:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next, we have a special segment.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.38,0:00:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chisaka, have you heard of the spring volleyball tournament?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.09,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's essentially nationals for volleyball, am I correct?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.96,0:00:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.02,0:00:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Recently, Miyagi Prefecture held \Ntheir qualifiers for the tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.52,0:00:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This year's matches seems to have had more drama than in previous years.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.73,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Indeed.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There are first-years who are making their debut on the national stage,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.10,0:00:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and third-years who are fighting their final battle in high school.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.01,0:00:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Each of them must have their own story.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.49,0:00:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today, we want to introduce to everyone these high school students who bet their youth on volleyball.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.31,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a stage for fierce battle.
