Dialogue: 5,0:01:03.20,0:01:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A place to bet one's youth on—a place to start a challenge.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.86,0:01:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All three years of high school are encapsulated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:37.99,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(892.5,370.5)\fscx47\fscy47\frz31.83\fry357.3\fax-0.59\fnFranklin Gothic Heavy\c&H9A6B76&\1a&H1F&\blur0.55\be1}J{\c&H9C707B&}a{\c&H9F7680&}p{\c&HA17B85&}a{\c&HA4818A&}n{\c&HA6868F&}e{\c&HA7868F&}s{\c&HA7858F&}e {\c&HA9848E&}Na{\c&HAA838E&}t{\c&HA9818C&}i{\c&HA87F89&}o{\c&HA67D87&}n{\c&HA57B84&}a{\c&HA47982&}l {\c&H9F7780&}H{\c&H9D767F&}i{\c&H9A757E&}g{\c&H98747D&}h {\c&H9C737B&}S{\c&H9E727A&}c{\c&HA07278&}h{\c&HA27277&}o{\c&HA47176&}o{\c&HA37176&}l {\c&HA17075&}V{\c&HA17074&}o{\c&HA07074&}l{\c&H9F7073&}l{\c&H9E7073&}e{\c&H9D6F73&}y{\c&H9C6F72&}b{\c&H9B6F72&}a{\c&H9B6F71&}l{\c&H9A6E71&}l {\c&H986E70&}T{\c&H9D6F71&}o{\c&HA27073&}u{\c&HA67174&}r{\c&HAB7275&}n{\c&HB07377&}a{\c&HB57478&}m{\c&HB6787A&}e{\c&HB87B7D&}n{\c&HB97F7F&}t
Dialogue: 5,0:01:34.08,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The National High School Volleyball Tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spring tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.53,0:01:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The stage where those who dream of making it in volleyball play.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.06,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}October. It's the beginning of the\N qualifiers for the spring tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.64,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koganegawa Kanji is a first-year at Date Tech High School.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.41,0:02:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's also one of the challengers aiming to win the spring tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.06,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although he has just started playing volleyball,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.33,0:02:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he's blessed with being 190 cm tall and having good reflexes.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.36,0:02:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serving as the team's on-court playmaker and setter,\N he is taking on the spring tournament for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:36.42,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017,408)\fscx46\fscy46\frz-4.66\fax0.07\fnpastel\c&HCBCEC0&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Mine West              Date Tech
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.46,0:02:36.42,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017,408)\fscx46\fscy46\frz-4.66\fax0.07\fnpastel\c&HCBCEC0&\blur1}Mine West              Date Tech
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.82,0:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Date Tech's specialty is undoubtedly...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}their blocking!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:49.02,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,223)\fscx96\fscy96\frz8.832\fax-0.15\fnBrush Strokes\fsp1.5\b1\c&H6A6849&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}The Iron Wall of Date
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.06,0:02:49.02,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,223)\fscx96\fscy96\frz8.832\fax-0.15\fnBrush Strokes\fsp1.5\b1\c&H6A6849&\blur1.3}The Iron Wall of Date
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.63,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The so-called "Iron Wall of Date" terrifies other schools.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the interhigh qualifiers taking place in summer,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.84,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everyone has high expectations for the giant setter Koganegawa because the third-years have retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(164,757)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H14161A&\3c&H14161A&\blur1.01}Q: {\bord2.5}Are you stressed?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(164,757)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HBBBDC1&\blur1.01}Q: Are you stressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(0,0)\c&HFAFCFC&\blur1\p1}m 155 792 l 1352 792 1352 1005 155 1005
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,836)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Date Tech High School
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,836)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\blur1.01}Date Tech High School
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(834,950)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Setter {\fs100}Koganegawa Kanji {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(834,950)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\blur1.01}Setter {\fs100}Koganegawa Kanji {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.59,0:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right now, I'm basically a baby as a setter!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But since this important task is\N entrusted to me, I will try my best!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.84,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a first-year and a starter, \Nhe will take on nationals for the first time.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.99,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can hear some tension in his words.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Miyagi Prefecture qualifiers for the spring tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.83,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only one school can advance \Nthrough the strait gate to nationals.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Date Tech has demonstrated their tough defense and started off strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:42.12,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,761)\fscx96\fscy96\frz8.766\fax-0.3\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H2B2D2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Shirato                            {\fax-0.15\c&H474445&}Date Tech
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.86,0:03:42.12,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,761)\fscx96\fscy96\frz8.766\fax-0.3\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H2B2D2A&\1a&H0F&\blur1.01}Shirato                            {\fax-0.15\c&H474445&}Date Tech
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.63,0:03:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They have also won the first round of the 16-team tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.52,0:03:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then comes the quarterfinals.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.51,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their opponent is the talented Aoba Jousai High School.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.64,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it's because he was nervous for his first spring tournament,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Koganegawa's movements \Nbecame even stiffer than before.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.17,0:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But with the help of his seniors,\N he slowly returned to his usual form.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, in the end,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.22,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koganegawa's block was broken through by his opponent, and the match was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.66,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976.5,885)\fscx115\fscy115\frz0.348\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H383838&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Date Tech             Aoba Jousai
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.66,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976.5,885)\fscx115\fscy115\frz0.348\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H383838&\1a&H14&\blur1.01}Date Tech             Aoba Jousai
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.77,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for messing up!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But next time,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.61,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to become the third section \Nof the Iron Wall so that we can return here!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His first attempt at the spring tournament ended so swiftly.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.45,0:04:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, his story is just getting started.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world of competition is ruthless.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.96,0:05:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there is a loser, there must be a winner on the other side.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.89,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Date Tech High School was defeated by one of the\N favorites for the tournament, Aoba Jousai High School.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Miyagi Prefecture's best setter,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.31,0:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oikawa creates a style of volleyball based on combo attacks with his diverse sets.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Aoba Jousai's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.76,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,206)\frz0.41\fnpastel\c&HDBDDCB&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Team A               Team B
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.76,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,206)\frz0.41\fnpastel\c&HDBDDCB&\blur1.01}Team A               Team B
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, come here for a moment.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.37,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During practice, Coach Irihata hardly speaks.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.17,0:05:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Instead, the third-years, led by their \Ncaptain Oikawa, actively drive the team.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The qualifiers are only two weeks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:54.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(344,789)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H14161A&\3c&H14161A&\blur1.01}Q: {\bord2.5}Thoughts on the spring tournament?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.11,0:05:54.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(344,789)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HBBBDC1&\blur1.01}Q: Thoughts on the spring tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:54.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(691,857)\c&HFDFDFD&\blur1\p1}m -355 -46 l 1015 -46 1015 124 -355 124
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.11,0:05:54.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(691,857)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Aoba Jousai High School
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.11,0:05:54.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(691,857)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\blur1.01}Aoba Jousai High School
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.11,0:05:54.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1261,928)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Setter {\fs100}Oikawa Tooru {\fs75}(third-year)
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.11,0:05:54.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1261,928)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H3D3D3D&\blur1.01}Setter {\fs100}Oikawa Tooru {\fs75}(third-year)
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We know exactly what we need to do.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And who we need to defeat.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's now past 8 pm.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.64,0:06:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, they keep practicing.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.70,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where does their passion come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.89,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,673.5)\frz15.32\fax-0.3\fnBrush Strokes\c&HEFEEEF&\blur1.2}Unstoppable Force
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.84,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The persistence needed to take down Shiratorizawa Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:14.23,signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.2\fax0.35\fnKomika Slick\b1\c&HE2E2E2&\alpha&HD0&\blur5\pos(1042.2,637.8)}Rule the Court
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.89,0:06:14.23,signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.2\fax0.35\fnKomika Slick\b1\c&HE2E2E2&\blur1.1\pos(1042.2,637.8)}Rule the Court
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.51,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although Shiratorizawa are the undisputed champions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982.5,809)\fscx115\fscy115\frz0.348\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H383838&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Aoba Jousai            Shiratorizawa
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982.5,809)\fscx115\fscy115\frz0.348\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H383838&\1a&H14&\blur1.01}Aoba Jousai            Shiratorizawa
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.10,0:06:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aoba Jousai never stops challenging them.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.09,0:06:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the interhigh qualifiers in the summer, the two sides met in the finals.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.26,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that wall was too thick.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.91,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now here in the spring tournament qualifiers,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.04,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the third-years, it's their last chance for revenge.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The semifinals approach.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their opponent is Miyagi Prefectural Karasuno High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.40,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,696)\fscx81\fscy81\frz0.029\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H313231&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5\be1}Karasuno                    {\c&H383938&}Aoba Jousai
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.40,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,696)\fscx81\fscy81\frz0.029\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H313231&\1a&H14&\blur0.55\be1}Karasuno                    {\c&H383938&}Aoba Jousai
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.05,0:07:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They defeated Karasuno in the third round of the interhigh qualifiers.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as they win this match, they can play Shiratorizawa.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.95,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, in the first set, under the onslaught of Karasuno, they could only defend passively and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.85,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,880.5)\fscx108\fscy108\frz357.4\fry3\fax0.05\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H2D2D2D&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5\be1}Karasuno                    {\c&H333A39&}Aoba Jousai
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.85,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,880.5)\fscx108\fscy108\frz357.4\fry3\fax0.05\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H2D2D2D&\1a&H14&\blur0.55\be1}Karasuno                    {\c&H333A39&}Aoba Jousai
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.43,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite this, due to their extensive experience, Aoba Jousai did not become anxious.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.38,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They never doubted what they believe in and kept playing their own style.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The match seesawed back and forth.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, they reached the third and final set.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.67,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After an endless deuce, the levy finally broke.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dream of taking on nationals ended.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.43,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oikawa's best attempt at setting up a play was shut down.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.04,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were unable to challenge Shiratorizawa,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Oikawa's challenge for the spring tournament ended here.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet he kept his head held high and looked straight forward.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate that we lost,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.61,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have faith our juniors will avenge us next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.51,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(975,142.5)\fscx43\fscy43\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H353432&\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5}The Japanese National High School Boys' Volleyball Tournament Miyagi Prefecture Qualifier
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.51,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(975,142.5)\fscx43\fscy43\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H353432&\1a&H0F&\blur0.5\be1}The Japanese National High School Boys' Volleyball Tournament Miyagi Prefecture Qualifier
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.51,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(973.5,280.5)\fscx68\fscy68\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H2F2D2B&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Finals
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.51,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(973.5,280.5)\fscx68\fscy68\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H2F2D2B&\1a&H0F&\blur1.01}Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.51,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(987,577.5)\fscx95\fscy95\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H2F2D2B&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Shiratorizawa \Nvs. \NKarasuno
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.51,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(987,577.5)\fscx95\fscy95\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H2F2D2B&\1a&H0F&\blur1.01}Shiratorizawa \Nvs. \NKarasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.77,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then comes the match that opens up the path to nationals: the finals.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Facing Karasuno, who keep on winning,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are the undisputed champions, Shiratorizawa,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.39,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}known all across the country after racking up \Ncountless victories via their overwhelming strength.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.47,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one doubted that Shiratorizawa would be victorious.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But within the match, there was a twist in the story.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.05,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the fierce battle in the final set, the champions, Shiratorizawa, were defeated by Karasuno.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First it was Aoba Jousai.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now Karasuno High School has upset Shiratorizawa,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}punching their ticket to nationals.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.09,0:10:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were once called "the fallen champs" and "the clipped crows."
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the secret that let them take flight?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.72,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Karasuno High School, \Nwho qualified for the spring tournament,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is an extremely ordinary public high school.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.12,0:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were once called "the fallen champs" and "the clipped crows."
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.07,0:10:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where can the secret to their newfound flight be found?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are currently 12 members on the team.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although it can't be called a big team,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.05,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after watching their practice, the first thing that can be noticed is their excellent teamwork.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.25,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how difficult the moment, Captain Sawamura shouts louder and clearer than everyone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Use your voices!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yessir!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.69,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's continue!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.97,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then there is Sugawara, \Nwho assists the sometimes harsh Sawamura.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't lose to Daichi!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then there's the life of the party, Tanaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.52,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Nishinoya, who uses his energetic \Nperformances to motivate his teammates.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ryuu, are you afraid of the cameras?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was weak!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:37.26,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(586,870)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H14161A&\3c&H14161A&\blur0.8}Q: {\bord2.5}Why has Karasuno taken flight?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.32,0:11:37.26,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(586,870)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HE0E0E0&\blur0.8}Q: Why has Karasuno taken flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:37.26,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(1116,950)\c&HFDFDFD&\blur1\p1}m -555 -57 l 539 -57 539 65 -555 65
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.32,0:11:37.26,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1116,950)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Karasuno High School Coach {\fs100}Ukai Keishin
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.32,0:11:37.26,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1116,950)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Karasuno High School Coach {\fs100}Ukai Keishin
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, the first-years all have spunk.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.49,0:11:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, three of the four first-years are starters.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.26,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Maybe the team can make the most of their abilities because the upperclassmen paved the way for them.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.21,0:11:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surprisingly, they have three first-years as starters.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.51,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems the key to the crows taking flight lies within these four spunky first-years.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.34,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of them is Kageyama Tobio, \Nstarting setter despite being a first-year.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.18,0:12:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His amazing setting skills have been well-known since his time at the famous Kitagawa First Junior High.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.65,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in the match against Shiratorizawa, his sets were just as clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:23.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H14161A&\3c&H14161A&\blur0.8\pos(312,762)}Q: {\bord2.5}Any reflections on the Shiratorizawa match?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.29,0:12:23.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HD8D8DA&\blur0.8\pos(312,762)}Q: Any reflections on the Shiratorizawa match?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:23.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(619,841)\c&HFDFDFD&\blur1\p1}m -321 -47 l 882 -47 882 165 -321 165
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.29,0:12:23.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(619,841)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Karasuno High School
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.29,0:12:23.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(619,841)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Karasuno High School
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.29,0:12:23.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017,954)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Setter {\fs100}Kageyama Tobio {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.29,0:12:23.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017,954)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Setter {\fs100}Kageyama Tobio {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh, well, they were really good.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Um, can I get back to practice?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.89,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The second first-year is Tsukishima Kei, \Nthe tallest member of the team and a middle blocker.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.46,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's usually rather reserved and doesn't like having to deal with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:41.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(522,768)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H14161A&\3c&H14161A&\blur0.8}Q: {\bord2.5}Are you always that reserved?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.15,0:12:41.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(522,768)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HDCDFDE&\blur0.8}Q: Are you always that reserved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:41.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(829,843)\blur1\p1}m -322 -40 l 796 -40 796 154 -322 154
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.15,0:12:41.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(829,843)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Karasuno High School
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.15,0:12:41.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(829,843)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Karasuno High School
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.15,0:12:41.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,948)\fscx80\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Middle Blocker {\fs100}Tsukishima Kei {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.15,0:12:41.61,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,948)\fscx80\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Middle Blocker {\fs100}Tsukishima Kei {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.14,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah. I mean, uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, his performance in the match was full of passion,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.12,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in complete contrast to the attitude he shows on the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He kept jumping up to block, over and over.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until his fingers became scarred.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.18,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.43,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a block bet on the will of his teammates, as well as his own pride.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.34,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The third first-year is Yamaguchi Tadashi.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His position is pinch server.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.70,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He plays a critical role in turning the tables\N during a set where the opponent has momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:39.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(297,752)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H14161A&\3c&H14161A&\blur0.8}Q: {\bord2.5}Do you feel nervous?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.28,0:13:39.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(297,752)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HDCDFDE&\blur0.8}Q: Do you feel nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:39.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(603,833)\c&HFDFDFD&\blur1\p1}m -323 -46 l 893 -46 893 167 -323 167
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.28,0:13:39.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(603,833)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Karasuno High School
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.28,0:13:39.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(603,833)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Karasuno High School
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.28,0:13:39.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(893,947)\fscx80\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Middle Blocker {\fs100}Yamaguchi Tadashi {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.28,0:13:39.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(893,947)\fscx80\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Middle Blocker {\fs100}Yamaguchi Tadashi {\fs75}(first-year)
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh, yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.63,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But when I stand in position to serve, I tell myself that it's now or never.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A body that can't move freely,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}afraid what will happen if he fails.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, Yamaguchi overcame the fear...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by believing in himself!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.17,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The last first-year is Hinata Shouyou, a middle blocker.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.58,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although he's only 163 cm tall, \Nhe's shown he can put in the work to play that position.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.15,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He says he started playing volleyball because he admired the Little Giant.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.11,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, outside of volleyball, \Nhe's just your average high school student.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Hinata. Your turn.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill in the parentheses with a vegetable you hate and read it out loud.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.73,0:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The vegetable that I don't like is piiman!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called a "green pepper" in English.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.91,0:14:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said sounds like "pee man."
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But once he appears on the court,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Give it to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he takes flight!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He flies!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fly!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.28,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what crushes the idea; of the undisputed champions of Shiratorizawa is his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.62,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(676.5,616.5)\fscx74\fscy55\frz5.902\fax-0.3\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H373838&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Shiratorizawa
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.62,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(676.5,616.5)\fscx74\fscy55\frz5.902\fax-0.3\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H373838&\1a&H0F&\blur0.5\be1}Shiratorizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.62,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1195.5,568.5)\fscx74\fscy55\frz6.169\fax-0.08\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H373838&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Karasuno
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.62,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1195.5,568.5)\fscx74\fscy55\frz6.169\fax-0.08\fnlemon squeezy\fsp1.5\c&H373838&\1a&H0F&\blur0.5\be1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:43.09,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(769,125)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H090A0D&\3c&H090A0D&\blur0.8}Q: {\bord2.5}Any thoughts on the final point?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.62,0:15:43.09,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(769,125)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HDCDFDE&\blur0.8}Q: Any thoughts on the final point?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushiwaka's cross-court spike was sick!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.92,0:15:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When planning that final attack, I waited patiently at first, and then rushed forward with everyone with a "bam"!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.48,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where they cultivate teamwork isn't limited to the court or the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:57.10,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(926,251)\fscx51\fscy51\frz-10.78\fax0.3\fnScratch\b1\shad1.5\c&H292F23&\4c&H21241B&\blur1.2}F{\c&H293024&}o{\c&H2A3024&\4c&H21251B&}o{\c&H2A3125&\4c&H22251B&}t {\c&H2B3326&\4c&H22261C&}o{\c&H2C3427&}f {\c&H2C3528&\4c&H22271C&}t{\c&H2D3629&\4c&H23271C&}h{\c&H2D362A&\4c&H23281C&}e {\c&H2E382B&}S{\c&H2F392C&\4c&H23291D&}l{\c&H2F3A2D&\4c&H24291D&}o{\c&H303A2D&\4c&H242A1D&}p{\c&H303B2E&}e
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry home after eating.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:02.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1097,142)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H090A0D&\3c&H090A0D&\blur0.8}Q: {\bord2.5}What about dinner?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.10,0:16:02.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1097,142)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HDCDFDE&\blur0.8}Q: What about dinner?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll eat dinner when I get back!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a snack!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.81,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's take a look at how Hinata scarfs down his food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:13.28,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(215,207)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H090A0D&\3c&H090A0D&\blur0.8}Q: {\bord2.5}Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.81,0:16:13.28,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(215,207)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HDCDFDE&\blur0.8}Q: Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.03,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He truly is a Little Giant.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! The meat buns that the \Ncaptain treats us to are awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.88,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I didn't say anything about paying for them!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, today it'll be my treat.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Daichi, can you cover me too?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say to eat after paying?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.92,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coach, please treat us this time to celebrate our victory!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.01,0:16:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The key to Karasuno High School's flight seems to be the relationship between the seniors and juniors—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.84,0:16:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an environment where you can play together happily.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.02,0:16:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this way, Karasuno High School set off a whirlwind\N in the tournament and printed their ticket to nationals.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In their hearts, there is a dream that needs to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.95,signs,,0,0,0,,{=0}{\move(958,308,958,-115.3,27,1612)\fscx53\fscy53\frz359\fax0.02\fnLucida Bright\b1\xshad2\yshad-1\c&HB8BEBB&\4c&H2C322D&\4a&H32&\blur1.2}Nekoma\NMetropolitan\NHigh School
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nekoma Metropolitan High School.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.14,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A powerhouse school in the tough division of Tokyo, they've advanced to national numerous times.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're led by Coach Nekomata,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.36,0:17:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who was rivals with the former Karasuno \Ncoach that led them to nationals, Ukai Ikkei.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.85,0:17:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The two teams have always been rivals and held a training camp together during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.14,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But despite having such a long relationship,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.58,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the two schools have never played \Nagainst each other in an official match.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.73,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}May they one day face off against each other at nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:44.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(396,742)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\bord3.5\c&H090A0D&\3c&H090A0D&\blur0.8}Q: {\bord2.5}Can you say a few words to Karasuno?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.11,0:17:44.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(396,742)\fnFranklin Gothic Book\c&HDCDFDE&\blur0.8}Q: Can you say a few words to Karasuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:44.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(876,816)\c&HFDFDFD&\blur1\p1}m -518 -48 l 674 -48 674 170 -518 170
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.11,0:17:44.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(876,816)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Nekoma Metropolitan High School
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.11,0:17:44.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(876,816)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Nekoma Metropolitan High School
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.11,0:17:44.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,937)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Captain {\fs100}Kuroo Tetsurou {\fs75}(third-year)
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.11,0:17:44.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,937)\fscx85\fscy85\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\c&H2A2A2A&\blur1.01}Captain {\fs100}Kuroo Tetsurou {\fs75}(third-year)
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Congrats on advancing to the spring tournament.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.82,0:17:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll definitely win the Tokyo qualifiers and make the Battle of the Garbage Dumpster a reality.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.36,0:17:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will the goddess of battle let these \Ntwo fated schools meet on the court?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.54,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tokyo qualifiers start in November.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna win the spring tournament!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.77,0:18:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever eager to improve, the players have a passionate soul.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the reward for their diligent efforts.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spring tournament's orange court—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.56,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the stage where dreams of youth are made or broken.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rivals who fight hard on the court
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.76,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are also buddies who share the same dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.96,0:19:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that dream on its wings, the crow now takes flight!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.90,0:19:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, your youth really is a special time.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of my high school days.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, me too.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.72,0:20:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that Karasuno High School can work hard on behalf of their defeated opponents.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We hope you were satisfied with today's special.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.54,0:20:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to your feedback.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.12,0:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's over?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.43,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We will draw a name from among those who provide feedback to win a special sticker made for—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was barely in it at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just mentioned in passing when they were introducing our team.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My name wasn't even mentioned.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get to you, Asahi.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is to spike the ball.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.05,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kageyama, you looked so unfriendly. It creeped me out!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What'd you say, moron?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon. Let's get back to practice.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.94,0:20:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.44,0:20:56.44,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
